01:01:20,620 --> 01:01:24,620
Probably a two there.

1393
01:01:24,620 --> 01:01:26,620
This is Hooke's Law.

1394
01:01:26,620 --> 01:01:28,620
This is Hooke's Law.

1395
01:01:28,620 --> 01:01:31,620
The energy stored in a stretched spring

1396
01:01:31,620 --> 01:01:36,620
