1397
01:01:36,620 --> 01:01:37,620
That's the Hooke's Law.

1398
01:01:37,620 --> 01:01:40,620
The formula for the...

1399
01:01:40,620 --> 01:01:44,620
Now, what happens when you go to the continuum limit?

1400
