01:04:15,620 --> 01:04:16,620
It doesn't matter what.

1464
01:04:16,620 --> 01:04:17,620
It's just x dot squared.

1465
01:04:17,620 --> 01:04:19,620
It's clearly kinetic energy.

1466
01:04:19,620 --> 01:04:20,620
What about this term here?

1467
01:04:20,620 --> 01:04:22,620
What's that going to look like?

1468
01:04:22,620 --> 01:04:24,620
How about xi minus xi plus one?

