1470
01:04:27,620 --> 01:04:28,620
Derivative.

1471
01:04:28,620 --> 01:04:29,620
Derivative.

1472
01:04:29,620 --> 01:04:32,120
This is like the derivative

1473
01:04:32,120 --> 01:04:34,620
