1476
01:04:41,620 --> 01:04:44,620
This is derivative of x with respect to time.

1477
01:04:44,620 --> 01:04:49,620
This is derivative of x with respect to sigma squared.

1478
01:04:49,620 --> 01:04:51,620
This is the energy of the string.

1479
01:04:51,620 --> 01:04:53,620
If I wanted to write the Lagrangian,

