01:05:03,620 --> 01:05:04,620
So, this is the energy of the string.

1484
01:05:04,620 --> 01:05:06,620
This is potential energy.

1485
01:05:06,620 --> 01:05:09,620
Lagrangian is kinetic energy minus.

1486
01:05:09,620 --> 01:05:13,620
So, if I wanted the Lagrangian,

1487
01:05:13,620 --> 01:05:16,620
it would be this.

1488
01:05:16,620 --> 01:05:17,620
If I wanted the energy,

1489
01:05:17,620 --> 01:05:20,620
it would be with a plus sign.

1490
01:05:20,620 --> 01:05:21,620
I'll write the energy.

1491
01:05:21,620 --> 01:05:26,620
We'll write the energy.

1492
01:05:26,620 --> 01:05:32,620
Hamiltonian plus.

1493
01:05:32,620 --> 01:05:35,620
Let's focus for a little bit.

1494
01:05:35,620 --> 01:05:38,120
I'm going to stop in a

1495
01:05:38,120 --> 01:05:40,620
