1504
01:06:08,620 --> 01:06:11,620
but in which there are only two x's.

1505
01:06:11,620 --> 01:06:14,620
The two x's moving in

1506
01:06:14,620 --> 01:06:17,620
the direction perpendicular to the motion.

1507
01:06:17,620 --> 01:06:19,620
So, this could be called x and y,

1508
01:06:19,620 --> 01:06:21,620
