01:06:28,620 --> 01:06:30,620
Is that clear?

1514
01:06:30,620 --> 01:06:33,620
Yeah, okay.

1515
01:06:33,620 --> 01:06:35,620
Oh, I just absorbed it.

1516
01:06:35,620 --> 01:06:37,620
I just chose...

1517
01:06:37,620 --> 01:06:38,620
Oh, sorry, there is a two.

