1921
01:22:57,620 --> 01:23:01,620
whose potential energy is proportional to their length.

1922
01:23:01,620 --> 01:23:03,620
That's something we actually could

1923
01:23:03,620 --> 01:23:05,620
have deduced directly from here.

1924
01:23:05,620 --> 01:23:07,620
In fact, why am I saying we could have?

1925
01:23:07,620 --> 01:23:09,620
I mean, we could have deduced that

1926
01:23:09,620 --> 01:23:12,620
