1949
01:24:05,620 --> 01:24:07,620
not the mass.

1950
01:24:07,620 --> 01:24:09,620
Okay?

1951
01:24:09,620 --> 01:24:11,620
That, if you remember, came

1952
01:24:11,620 --> 01:24:13,620
