01:24:35,620 --> 01:24:37,620
So when you do that, and

1963
01:24:37,620 --> 01:24:39,620
you go through this little exercise,

1964
01:24:39,620 --> 01:24:44,620
your conclusion is that the Hooke's law energy

1965
01:24:44,620 --> 01:24:47,620
of the effective non-relativistic string

1966
01:24:47,620 --> 01:24:50,620
should be identified with the mass squared,

1967
01:24:50,620 --> 01:24:52,620
which indirectly tells you that

1968
