the rest mass of the string

1969
01:24:54,620 --> 01:24:57,620
is proportional to its length.

1970
01:24:57,620 --> 01:25:00,620
And finally, there are lots and lots of field theory

1971
01:25:00,620 --> 01:25:03,620
and condensed matter systems which have the same property,

