01:27:59,620 --> 01:28:00,620
Okay?

2041
01:28:00,620 --> 01:28:01,620
Squared.

2042
01:28:02,620 --> 01:28:06,620
Which is equal to m, which really means mc squared,

2043
01:28:06,620 --> 01:28:09,620
