2044
01:28:10,620 --> 01:28:14,620
So, in that context, the internal energy

2045
01:28:14,620 --> 01:28:18,620
when the particle is at rest in space

2046
01:28:18,620 --> 01:28:21,620
is proportional to the mass.

2047
01:28:21,620 --> 01:28:23,620
That's your good old e equals mc squared.

2048
01:28:23,620 --> 01:28:24,620
Okay.

2049
01:28:24,620 --> 01:28:27,120
And that tells you that for

2050
01:28:27,120 --> 01:28:29,620
a particle at rest, it's inertia.

2051
01:28:29,620 --> 01:28:31,620
A particle at rest, it's inertia.

2052
01:28:31,620 --> 01:28:36,620
In other words, its usual resistance to acceleration

2053
01:28:36,620 --> 01:28:41,620
